project.name: vee
project.notes: This is the project which started it all. After an example by E. Paul Goldenberg. Featuring recursion without the need for a base case and first class custom blocks it was Brian's demo at the 2008 Scratch conference, why Scratch needed custom procedures.To this day, Vee is the first project we test whenever we change anything or add new features to Snap.
